SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT VIRTLWARTERAUM.AUFTNR, CONVERT(smallint, HOTLINE.Event) AS HotEvent, CONVERT(smallint, HOTLINE.Prioritaet) AS HotPrio, HOTLINE_BEHEBUNG.Fehlertext, HOTLINE.Job_beendet, VIRTLWARTERAUM.TKNR, '' AS Uhrzeit, '' AS Datum, KUNDEN.Matchcode, HOTLINE.Stichwort, HOTLINE.derzeitige_Aktion, HOTLINE.derzeitiger_Status, HOTLINE.Ansprechpartner, HOTLINE.Anbahnung, Z_ANBAHNUNG.Beschreibung AS BeschrAnbahnung, Z_ANBAHNUNG.Wahrscheinlichkeit, Z_ANBAHNUNG.GeschaetztesAbschlussdatum FROM VIRTLWARTERAUM WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN WARTERAUM WITH(NOLOCK) ON VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene1 = WARTERAUM.Ebene1 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene2 = WARTERAUM.Ebene2 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene3 = WARTERAUM.Ebene3 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene4 = WARTERAUM.Ebene4 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.Warteraum = WARTERAUM.Warteraum_Nr INNER JOIN HOTLINE WITH(NOLOCK) ON VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene1 = HOTLINE.Ebene1 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene2 = HOTLINE.Ebene2 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene3 = HOTLINE.Ebene3 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene4 = HOTLINE.Ebene4 AND VIRTLWARTERAUM.AUFTNR = HOTLINE.lfd_Job_Nr LEFT OUTER JOIN Z_ANBAHNUNG WITH(NOLOCK) ON HOTLINE.Ebene1 = Z_ANBAHNUNG.Ebene1 AND HOTLINE.Ebene2 = Z_ANBAHNUNG.Ebene2 AND HOTLINE.Ebene3 = Z_ANBAHNUNG.Ebene3 AND HOTLINE.Ebene4 = Z_ANBAHNUNG.Ebene4 AND HOTLINE.Anbahnung = Z_ANBAHNUNG.AnbahnungsNr LEFT OUTER JOIN HOTLINE_BEHEBUNG WITH(NOLOCK) ON HOTLINE.Ebene1 = HOTLINE_BEHEBUNG.Ebene1 AND HOTLINE.Ebene2 = HOTLINE_BEHEBUNG.Ebene2 AND HOTLINE.Ebene3 = HOTLINE_BEHEBUNG.Ebene3 AND HOTLINE.Ebene4 = HOTLINE_BEHEBUNG.Ebene4 AND HOTLINE.lfd_Job_Nr = HOTLINE_BEHEBUNG.HotlineNummer LEFT OUTER JOIN KUNDEN WITH(NOLOCK) ON HOTLINE.Ebene1 = KUNDEN.Ebene1 AND HOTLINE.Ebene2 = KUNDEN.Ebene2 AND HOTLINE.Ebene3 = KUNDEN.Ebene3 AND HOTLINE.Ebene4 = KUNDEN.Ebene4 AND HOTLINE.KundenNr = KUNDEN.KDNR WHERE (VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene1 = :1) AND (VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene2 = :2) AND (VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene3 = :3) AND (VIRTLWARTERAUM.Ebene4 = :4) AND (VIRTLWARTERAUM.Warteraum = :5) AND Hotline.Job_Beendet=:7 :6
